{"title":"淮河上的故事","authors":["池牧阳"],"dates":[{"year":1949,"month":9,"day":21}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河上的故事"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"池牧阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨的太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着金黄的淮河水；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照着刘老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老头"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"撒网在淮河上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽然，一阵枪响，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的保安队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来到了淮河边……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保安队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亮出刺刀来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对准了刘老头的心口，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指着北岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“说！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那边村里有多少解"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"放军”？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没扯过谎；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他看看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保安队顶多不过四百人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里的石头才落了地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不多，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只二十个”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保安队，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"希望这话是真，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但又怕这话假，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上去就给他一枪把。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老头涨红了脸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“真的，真的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有二十个”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但心里却想："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你们这些快落网的鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看还能翻起多大浪”！？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保安队开向北岸去了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"淮河北岸"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"起了战争；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战争的结果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们添了一个新兵营。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人称赞刘老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人都说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“刘老头聪明”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老头却笑笑："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“我打一辈子鱼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不懂别的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只知道："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱吃什么饵；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钓多大的鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"该用多大的钩”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但俘虏兵看见刘老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“死老头子撒谎”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘老头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昂着脖子讲："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“对你们说实话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还有咱们活的呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这回"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就算咱吃一辈子清斋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"临死喝碗狗肉汤”！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}